Want to enhance your reels with my LUTs?

Comment “LUT” and I’ll send you a free course that includes:

- 8 lessons on growing and monetizing on Instagram
- 2 ready-to-use LUTs for your content

Reminder: Shoot in good lighting—LUTs won’t fix poor video quality.

caption.text:
The Main Difference ⬇️

Here’s the thing: luck can sometimes play a role, but you can increase your chances if you know a few key strategies to help you go viral:

1️⃣ Grab Attention - Both reels can have the same hook, but you also need great visuals that are clear and high quality. 

Focus on the first 3 seconds of your reel. Ensure that the visuals and hook instantly engage the audience. Allocate 80% of your time here, as it matters most.

2️⃣ Maximize Watch Time - Once you catch someone’s attention, you need to keep it until the end. (That’s what all viral reels does).

The easiest way to do this is to create shorter reels, around 5-8 seconds. Aim for 90% watch time consistently on these short videos.

3️⃣ Follow Trends - Sometimes, you can do everything right, but you won’t get the same number of views if you’re too late to the trend. 

Always stay up to date with trends to see better results with your reels.

⚡️ Consistently combining these elements in your new reels, regardless of your posting frequency, will eventually help you go VIRAL! 

Just make sure not to post fewer than 4 reels per week to avoid losing momentum.

🤫 This is exactly what I teach inside Instagram Secrets.

🧠 It also includes content research and editing tutorials to show you how I create and edit top-notch reel ideas!

👉 DM or comment “Grow” for instant access to the full program, absolutely free!

caption.text:
If you’re a content creator struggling to grow, you might need fresh feedback.

The best feedback comes from learning from others, but it’s hard to access these opportunities without your own results.

That’s why I created the Instagram Secrets course—to share my insights from growing past 500K followers.

Want free access? Comment “Grow” and I’ll send it to you right away.

caption.text:
How to create viral reels:

Share this with someone who is struggling to grow on Instagram 🖤

Step 1: Comment “Template” to receive the entire Viral Hooks Database.

Step 2: Open the database and select your hooks.

Step 3: Go to ChatGPT and type:

“Tailor these hooks for a fitness niche centered around helping people lose weight.”

Then copy and paste the hooks you’ve selected.

Enjoy. 🙏

caption.text:
Here’s how to shoot dark aesthetics on your iPhone camera:

P.S: I’m giving away an Aesthetic Content Bank and a free course to help you create viral reels!

Comment the word “CONTENT” and I’ll send it to you ASAP. 🙏

Here’s how you can make your content look dark and aesthetic: 👇

1. Set your camera to 4K at 30 or 60 fps (you’ll find these options in the top right-hand corner or in your camera settings).

2. Swipe up on the camera and lower the exposure to -1.0 (this is just my preference).

3. Tap on the lightest part of the screen and adjust the brightness by swiping up or down.

Enjoy!

reusable_text_info.text: MY SECRET FORMULA TO GO VIRAL EVERY TIME YOU POST

caption.text:
Comment “STRATEGY” for the free training that shows how I got millions of views on my reels. 👇 

It’s frustrating when your content doesn’t reach non-followers. 

So here’s what you need to do before your next post:

1. Go to your explore page.

2. Type in the topic of your reel, like “Gaining muscle”.

3. Scroll to the reels tab.

4. Look for reels with over a million views.

5. For instance, I found one with 1.6 million views, so I’m going to examine its hook.

6. This reel’s hook was “I’m scared to gain weight”.

7. I would then create my OWN version of that reel.

8. If I gained weight, I’d use the same hook and show before and after shots.

9. Then, publish it.

This viral reel reaching 1.6 million people indicates another similar reel could also go viral.

Give it a try and let me know how it works out!

caption.text:
Use it WISELY 🤫👇

The hook is one of the most crucial elements for top-performing reels.

In the last 12 months, I gained 300,000 followers for my personal brand—all thanks to using the right hooks!

Here’s my top-performing hook and the total number of views it got:

“By age 22, you should be smart enough to know this…” – 15M+ total views

P.S.: You can adapt this hook for any niche by following the formula.

For example:

“By age 22, you should be smart enough to know this leg exercise…”
“By age 22, you should be smart enough to know this productivity technique…”

The first 3 seconds of your video are critical: it’s the moment you either grab the viewer’s attention or lose it.

Start your videos with strong, powerful hooks ✨. I dive deeper into this in my Viral Reels Secrets program.

Comment “Viral” and I’ll send you free access to this program.

See you inside 🤍
